      "content": "advice doesnt really help when the entire foundation of your life is just dead. it's not like i'm just \"sad\" or something. it's like the version of me that existed is just gone. i feel like a ghost just walking around. what am i supposed to do with a life that doesn't even feel like mine anymore? it just feels like a heavy weight i have to carry every single day for no reason.",
